   // Register a new crop block
   BlockRegistry.register(new CropBlock(Registry.register(Registry.BLOCK, new Identifier("harvest_harmony", "rare_herb"), Block.builder()
           .material(Material.CROP)
           .sound(SoundRegistry.get(SoundType.PLANT).getSoundGroup())
           .defaultState(getDefaultState())
           .build()).setRegistryName(new Identifier("harvest_harmony", "rare_herb")));
   ```

2. **Recipe Registration:**
   ```java
   // Register a new recipe for a salad
   CraftingHandler.addShapedRecipe(
       RecipeCategory.CRAFTING,
       new Identifier("harvest_harmony", "salad"),
       ItemStack.of(Items.SALAD),
       6,
       new ItemAndAmount(new ItemStack(Registry.ITEM.get(new Identifier("harvest_harmony", "rare_ingredient")), 1)),
       new ItemAndAmount(new ItemStack(Items.BEANS), 2)
   );
   ```

